---
const heroTrust = ['Donativos em espécie', 'Voluntariado', 'Famílias FAT', 'Apoio financeiro'];
---

<section id="inicio" class="relative isolate overflow-hidden px-5 py-16 sm:px-8 lg:py-24" aria-labelledby="hero-heading">
  <div class="ambient-blob -right-20 top-10 h-72 w-72 bg-playful-orange/45"></div>
  <div class="ambient-blob -left-24 bottom-8 h-80 w-80 bg-playful-peach/80"></div>

  <div class="mx-auto grid max-w-7xl items-center gap-12 lg:grid-cols-[1.02fr_0.98fr]">
    <div class="relative z-10 text-center lg:text-left">
      <div data-reveal="left" data-reveal-delay="40" class="mb-6 inline-flex -rotate-2 items-center gap-2 rounded-full border border-playful-line bg-playful-peach px-4 py-2 text-sm font-extrabold text-playful-orange-dark shadow-pillowy">
        <span aria-hidden="true">🐾</span>
        <span>Faça a Diferença</span>
      </div>

      <h1 id="hero-heading" data-reveal="left" data-reveal-delay="120" class="font-playful-display text-[3.05rem] font-extrabold leading-[0.95] tracking-[-0.055em] text-playful-orange-dark sm:text-6xl lg:text-7xl">
        Apoie o
        <span class="relative mx-1 inline-block text-playful-orange">
          CAPA PVL!
          <svg class="absolute -bottom-3 left-0 h-4 w-full text-playful-watermelon/70" viewBox="0 0 220 20" aria-hidden="true" preserveAspectRatio="none">
            <path d="M4 13C52 4 107 3 216 12" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-width="8" />
          </svg>
        </span>
      </h1>

      <p data-reveal="left" data-reveal-delay="210" class="mx-auto mt-7 max-w-2xl text-lg font-medium leading-8 text-playful-muted lg:mx-0">
        Cada gesto conta. Seja com o seu tempo, com materiais ou com uma contribuição financeira,
        a sua ajuda transforma a vida de centenas de animais todos os anos.
      </p>
      <p data-reveal="left" data-reveal-delay="270" class="mx-auto mt-4 max-w-xl text-base font-medium leading-7 text-playful-muted/85 lg:mx-0 sm:text-lg">
        Descubra como pode contribuir para o nosso trabalho e juntar-se à nossa comunidade de defensores animais.
      </p>

      <div data-reveal="left" data-reveal-delay="340" class="mt-8 flex flex-col justify-center gap-4 sm:flex-row lg:justify-start">
        <a href="mailto:capa.geralpvl@gmail.com" class="squishy playful-focus inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 rounded-full bg-playful-orange px-8 py-4 font-playful-display text-base font-extrabold text-white shadow-squish">
          Fale Connosco
          <span aria-hidden="true">❤</span>
        </a>
        <a href="#donativos" class="squishy playful-focus inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 rounded-full border-2 border-playful-orange bg-white/80 px-8 py-4 font-playful-display text-base font-extrabold text-playful-orange-dark shadow-pillowy">
          Ver formas de ajudar
          <span aria-hidden="true">↓</span>
        </a>
      </div>

      <div data-reveal="pop" data-reveal-delay="430" class="mt-9 flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-3 lg:justify-start">
        {heroTrust.map((trust, index) => (
          <span class={`rounded-full border border-playful-line bg-white/78 px-4 py-2 text-sm font-bold text-playful-muted shadow-sm ${index === 0 ? '-rotate-2' : index === 1 ? 'rotate-1' : index === 2 ? '-rotate-1' : 'rotate-2'}`}>
            ✓ {trust}
          </span>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>

    <div data-reveal="hero-image" data-reveal-delay="180" class="relative z-10 mx-auto w-full max-w-[590px] pt-4 lg:pt-0">
      <div class="absolute -right-5 top-6 z-20 rotate-12 rounded-full bg-playful-watermelon px-4 py-4 text-white shadow-pillowy-lg" aria-hidden="true">❤</div>
      <div class="absolute -bottom-5 left-1/2 z-20 w-max -translate-x-1/2 -rotate-3 rounded-full bg-playful-peach px-5 py-3 text-sm font-extrabold text-playful-muted shadow-pillowy">
        Ajuda que chega ao abrigo
      </div>
      <picture class="relative block rotate-1">
        <source srcset="/images/ajudar/hero-playful-help.webp" type="image/webp" />
        <img
          src="/images/ajudar/hero-playful-help-fallback.jpg"
          alt="Cão feliz no abrigo, representando a ajuda ao CAPA"
          class="blob-mask aspect-[5/4] w-full border-8 border-white object-cover shadow-pillowy-lg"
          loading="eager"
          fetchpriority="high"
          width="1400"
          height="1120"
        />
      </picture>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
